description:
This is a 10 minute workout called 'Elliptical Workout Routine - Mind Over Munch' from the channel Mind Over Munch.
The workout falls under Cardio/Elliptical and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Other for this workout.
The workout has a The Meditative Grind and The Endorphin Wave vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Check out my favorite Elliptical workout routine! This cardio workout routine will get your heart rate up, and you won't get bored! Be sure to download the PDF to take with you to the gym on your phone or tablet, that way you can keep track!
